    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>最近不想用 elementui 这种组件，想着原生的 input 写表单验证的时候发现了 vee-validate 可以直接设定他的规则用起来也很简单在这里浅浅记录一下。</p><h1 id="在-vue2-导入-vee-validate"><a href="#在-vue2-导入-vee-validate" class="headerlink" title="在 vue2 导入 vee-validate"></a>在 vue2 导入 vee-validate</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn add vee-validate@3</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">npm install vee-validate@3 --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="用法"><a href="#用法" class="headerlink" title="用法"></a>用法</h2><p>在 main 里面导入</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">ValidationProvider</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;vee-validate&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title class_">Vue</span>.<span class="title function_">component</span>(<span class="string">&quot;ValidationProvider&quot;</span>, <span class="title class_">ValidationProvider</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 规则 方式一</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">extend</span>(<span class="string">&quot;secret&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">validate</span>: <span class="function">(<span class="params">value</span>) =&gt;</span> value === <span class="string">&quot;example&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="string">&quot;This is not the magic word&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 方式二，新建一个js文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="string">&quot;@/js/validation&quot;</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="validation-js-文件"><a href="#validation-js-文件" class="headerlink" title="validation.js 文件"></a>validation.js 文件</h2><p>其他的自带规则移步到 →<a href="https://vee-validate.logaretm.com/v3/guide/rules.html#rules">https://vee-validate.logaretm.com/v3/guide/rules.html#rules</a></p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; extend, configure &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;vee-validate&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; required, email &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;vee-validate/dist/rules&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 错误或者成功时设置样式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">configure</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">classes</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">valid</span>: <span class="string">&quot;is-valid&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">invalid</span>: <span class="string">&quot;is-invalid&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">dirty</span>: [<span class="string">&quot;is-dirty&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;is-dirty&quot;</span>], <span class="comment">// multiple classes per flag!</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// ...</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自定义</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">extend</span>(<span class="string">&quot;positive&quot;</span>, <span class="function">(<span class="params">value</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> value &gt;= <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 必填的就可以加上这个</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">extend</span>(<span class="string">&quot;required&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  ...required,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="string">&quot;This field is required&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 自带的有很多可以按需引入</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">extend</span>(<span class="string">&quot;email&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  ...email,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">message</span>: <span class="string">&quot;请输入正确的邮箱格式&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="页面用法"><a href="#页面用法" class="headerlink" title="页面用法"></a>页面用法</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ValidationObserver</span> <span class="attr">v-slot</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&#123; handleSubmit &#125;&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 提交时才验证成功才跳转 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span> @<span class="attr">submit.prevent</span>=<span class="string">&quot;handleSubmit(onSubmit)&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 多个规则可以用|隔开 例如 required|email --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ValidationProvider</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">      <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;E-mail&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">      <span class="attr">:rules</span>=<span class="string">&quot;required&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">      <span class="attr">v-slot</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&#123; errors,classes &#125;&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    &gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;control&quot;</span> <span class="attr">:class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;classes&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- input的 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">v-model</span>=<span class="string">&quot;firstName&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- select的 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">v-model</span>=<span class="string">&quot;value&quot;</span> <span class="attr">as</span>=<span class="string">&quot;select&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="attr">selected</span>=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>&gt;</span>‐ 請選擇 運送方式 ‐<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>&gt;</span>123<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">&lt;!-- 错误信息 --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123; errors[0] &#125;&#125;<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">span</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ValidationProvider</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">button</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;submit&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Submit<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ValidationObserver</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> &#123; <span class="title class_">ValidationProvider</span>, <span class="title class_">ValidationObserver</span> &#125; <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;vee-validate&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">components</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title class_">ValidationProvider</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title class_">ValidationObserver</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">data</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">firstName</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">methods</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_">onSubmit</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">console</span>.<span class="title function_">log</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;验证成功&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;style lang=&quot;scss&quot; scoped&gt;</span><br><span class="line">.control &#123;</span><br><span class="line">width: 100%;</span><br><span class="line">span &#123;</span><br><span class="line">display: block;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">input &#123;</span><br><span class="line">padding: 5px 10px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;.failed &#123;</span><br><span class="line">input &#123;</span><br><span class="line">border: 1px #eb0600 solid;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&amp;.passed &#123;</span><br><span class="line">input &#123;</span><br><span class="line">border: 1px #045929 solid;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.control.failed input,</span><br><span class="line">.control.failed span &#123;</span><br><span class="line">color: #eb0600;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.control.passed input,</span><br><span class="line">.control.passed span &#123;</span><br><span class="line">color: #045929;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
